  limit in low dimensional gapless systems''";"11 pages, 6 figures. The current version of the main paper
  arXiv:0706.0212 is not up to date according to the Nature Physics editorial
  policy";Nature Physics 4, 477 (2008) - supplementary info;10.1038/nphys963;;cond-mat.stat-mech cond-mat.mes-hall cond-mat.str-el;http://arxiv.org/licenses/nonexclusive-distrib/1.0/;"  Here we give detailed derivations and provide additional examples to the main
paper: arXiv:0706.0212. In particular, we discuss the scaling behavior of
