0810.2507;Vladimir Dzuba;T. H. Dinh, V. A. Dzuba, and V. V. Flambaum;Calculation of the spectra of the superheavy element Z=112;5 pages, 3 tables, no figures;Phys. Rev. A 78, 062502 (2008);10.1103/PhysRevA.78.054501;;physics.atom-ph;http://arxiv.org/licenses/nonexclusive-distrib/1.0/;"  Accurate ab initio calculations of the energy levels of the superheavy
